BeamerPresenter shows a PDF presentation to speaker and audience in a
multi-screen setup with various control options and extra information
for the speaker.

Features:
- draw, highlight and point on the presentation with tools selected per input device
- supports pressure sensitive stylus input and different draw styles (e.g. Wacom tablet)
- save drawings in format compatible with Xournal++
- videos and sounds linked from a PDF file
- slide transitions and basic animations
- fast slide changes and browsing due to compressed cache of slides (configurable cache size)
- modular, configurable user interface for maximal flexibility
- does not try to take the role of your window manager
